TI  - Returns to Scale, Euler's Theorem, and the Form of Production Functions
AU  - McElroy, F. W.
AB  - [By generalizing Euler's Theorem, the classes of production functions for which scale elasticity depends either on output level alone, or on factor proportions alone, are examined.]
